{"tid":1416601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去煲底發夢既入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:01:23.000Z","uid":209700,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cc97c20c477ca5c9af010617a89c552db4c68cba","tid":1416601,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:17:47.000Z","msg":"識人係入面負責做維修<br />\n<br />\n佢叫我同你地講 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪再噴d字落牆</span><br />\n每次噴完上面都會叫佢地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">清走</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">但係！！！</span></span><br />\n如果唔係噴字 係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">連儂牆</span></span>既話 就唔屬於<span style=\"color: red;\">損壞</span> 唔關<span style=\"color: red;\">維修事</span> <br />\n<br />\n佢地係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔會理</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以大家下次見到幅牆咁白咁靚 就唔好嘥咗佢 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">將佢變做官方連儂牆！</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3qRfx8Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3qRfx8Q.png&h=192cb4be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0vPHXAx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0vPHXAx.png&h=d58ba250&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbdd102ec1f1c93733dee264691abec0bd4446f0","tid":1416601,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:18:15.000Z","msg":"我冇野講！"},{"pid":"4712c08a71191e8617a6919f2e0f75cb2cd0e314","tid":1416601,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:19:05.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"883362b3c2bdea3c12b13be2ed050c9ff2d7a0c1","tid":1416601,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:19:29.000Z","msg":"自推十次先"},{"pid":"65614e7f3f517573e45d88bdeb79100e34297c9f","tid":1416601,"uid":209700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":